description:
Дом с Алисой — приложение, в котором удобно настраивать умный дом и управлять им даже в дороге. Подключайте лампочки, пылесосы, датчики и тысячи других устройств — и контролируйте их здесь или через колонку.

• ВСЁ В ОДНОМ ПРИЛОЖЕНИИ
Добавляйте и удаляйте самые разные устройства, от колонок с Алисой до кондиционеров, меняйте названия и расположение — и настраивайте, как вам нравится.

• УДАЛЁННОЕ УПРАВЛЕНИЕ
Дом под контролем, даже если вы далеко: скажем, по дороге на дачу можно заранее включить обогреватель.

• ОДНА КОМАНДА ДЛЯ ВСЕГО
Запускайте нескольких устройств одной фразой — например, «Алиса, скоро буду дома». Настройте сценарий, и по этой команде включится кондиционер, пылесос начнёт уборку, а в коридоре зажжётся свет.

• ДОМ, КОТОРЫЙ САМ О ВАС ЗАБОТИТСЯ
Подключайте датчики — к примеру, температуры и влажности, — и проверяйте, как дела дома. Создайте сценарий, добавьте обогреватель и что-нибудь ещё — и дом будет сам следить, чтобы в нём хорошо дышалось.

• РУТИННЫЕ ДЕЛА ПО РАСПИСАНИЮ
Поручите часть домашних дел Алисе. Достаточно один раз настроить расписание, и она будет сама поливать цветы и включать перед сном увлажнитель.

• СЦЕНАРИЙ В ОДНО КАСАНИЕ
Добавьте сценарий в виджет — и кнопка управления будет всегда под рукой, на главном экране телефона.

• ТЫСЯЧИ РАЗНЫХ УСТРОЙСТВ
Подключайте сколько угодно домашних приборов разных производителей: в магазине вы узнаете эти устройства по отметке «Работает с Алисой».

UPGRADE TO TINDER PLATINUM
Get most of Tinder’s premium features: join Tinder Platinum™ to get your likes prioritised with potential matches, send them a compliment before matching and more.

So what are you waiting for? Join millions of people worldwide! Tinder offers the most daters, increasing your chances of finding exactly what you're looking for. Download the best free dating app today!

description:
Alice AI: texts, neural network, fresh ideas, knowledge, Russian-language AI chat.

Powerful Yandex AI on your phone helps with everyday chores and tackles tasks for study, work, and creativity.

Explore what the neural network can do with Alice—everything you expect from a smart chat in Russian.

Alice AI is Yandex’s family of generative models that power Alice. It includes:
- Alice AI LLM — a language model for answering questions and generating text;
- Alice AI ART — an image model for creating visuals;
- Alice AI VLM — a multimodal vision-language model for analyzing images, answering questions, and solving image-related tasks.

Ask questions, write and edit text—the Alice AI neural network responds accurately and comprehensively, and can enrich answers with images and source links. Speak by voice or type in chat.

Work with files (DOC, DOCX, PDF, TXT), structure information, and turn it into clear, usable reports. The Alice AI assistant quickly extracts key insights.

Work with photos—recognize text in images, identify objects, and get fast visual analysis. The AI chat assistant can pull data from a receipt photo, explain what’s in a shot, and convert it into an editable text format for further use.

Solve complex problems—reasoning mode produces not just quick and detailed answers, but thoughtful conclusions. You get well-founded solutions with expert-level analysis.

Create compelling English-language copy, ask questions, translate, and edit. Yandex Alice’s AI assistant helps draft anything—from personal emails and school assignments to business proposals.

Find inspiration: generate new project ideas, run brainstorms, craft descriptions and messages, and build your own text templates. Let Alice handle the routine. The AI assistant can write a letter, a script for an event or talk, suggest a post title, or even a name for your pet.

Create images and AI video—Yandex ART generates visuals or animates photos on request. Alice helps you produce striking social posts, a logo, or a birthday card.

Use AI chat for professional work. The assistant helps with programming and code, offering multiple solution approaches. Alice AI teaches logic, explains logical problems clearly, and shares interesting facts. Get advice and recommendations on any topic—Alice answers in detail, suggests step-by-step actions, and helps you plan.

Ask questions, type text, attach photos, videos, and files—or talk through the camera in real time with Live Mode. With the Pro option, show Alice what you see in Live Mode and get instant answers and ideas. Just open the Alice AI app and point your phone’s camera at whatever you want to learn about.

Alice AI can be your guide to landmarks, your kitchen co-pilot for “what can I cook with this?”, or your stylist for picking shoes to match your trousers. Ask anything and switch topics as needed. The neural network keeps context, recognizes objects in the frame, and delivers fast, in-depth answers.

You can save your tesbihat with smart dhikr application which is designed as real tasbeeh counter that looks like a ring. You can use the mobile dhikr application for the names of ALLAH (c.c), Salat-ı Tefriciye and for Salaah Tesbihat. Tasbeeh application will record your all dhikrs.

Even you close Digital Tasbeeh Counter, the number of the dhikr will not erased. When you restart the aplication, the dhikr number will appear on the screen. You should press the button to pulse the number.

You can save your dhikrs as the number of dhikrs, date and the name of the dhikrs to press the save button. You don 't have to check the screen, because digital tasbeeh counter app will give you vibration warning. Digital Tasbeeh Counter has three buttons basically: counter button, saving button and pulse button.

You can adjust the vibration or colours from the buttons top on the screen. In addition to save the battary, you can use the application on night mode. Digital Tasbeeh Counter is free and you won't see any advertisement during dhikr.

Specifications

Even you close the aplication, you never loose the numbers of the dhikrs untill you press the pulse button.

You can save your all dhikrs with the names and dates.

You can customize Digital Tasbeeh Counter with themes.

The application will save the energy by the help of night mode option.

You can dhikr with out check the screen by the help of vibration (you can close the vibration).

You can check your ex dhikrs by name, date and numbers.

Sajda – The Complete Islamic App, Ad-Free Since 2012  
Trusted by over 4 million Muslims around the world

Sajda is your all-in-one companion for a focused, fulfilling worship experience. Free of ads for over a decade and loved by millions globally, Sajda helps you stay spiritually connected—wherever life takes you.

Whether you're checking prayer times at work, reading the Quran while commuting, or finding the Qibla while traveling, Sajda supports your daily worship with clarity and ease.

Why millions choose Sajda:

Prayer Times  
Accurate and scholar-approved prayer timings based on your location. Fully adjustable, with countdowns to the next salah.

Adhan Alerts  
Get ready for prayer with peaceful calls from the muezzin—or choose your own sound. Includes guided rak’ah prompts.

Quran  
Read the Holy Quran with translations and transliterations. Save favorite ayahs, add personal notes, and pick your font. Effortlessly resume where you left off.

Dhikr  
Count your daily dhikr with a built-in counter. Listen to beautiful du’a recitations and join group dhikr sessions. More features are on the way, inshaAllah.

Qibla Direction  
Use the animated compass or map view (standard or satellite) to instantly find the Qibla—no matter where you are.

Widgets & Prayer Calendar  
Keep prayer times on your home screen. Share personalized salah schedules with family and friends.

Live from Makkah  
Watch real-time broadcasts from Masjid al-Haram and feel spiritually closer to the heart of Islam.

More than an app — a global movement  
Sajda has been ad-free since day one. Our mission is to connect 1 billion Muslims through simple, meaningful digital worship. Upgrade to Sajda Plus for offline Quran access, exclusive recitations, and to support prayer education worldwide.

Download Sajda now  
Join millions of Muslims from Istanbul to Jakarta, Tashkent to Barcelona. Download today and experience your faith with focus.

• Xonadon egalari bilan uchrashuv: Ilova orqali sotib olmoqchi bo’lgan xonadoningizni ko'rish uchun uchrashuv bron qiling.Tajribali quruvchilar: Barcha xonadonlar ro'yxati ishonchli manbalardan olingan.

PURE is a dating app for curious people to show up in their most playful version of themselves. It’s a space to be honest with your intentions and clear in your boundaries.

Connect with like-minded community to create and explore new exciting experiences in a safe and supportive space.

Let your imagination go wild and get ready for amazing dates!

* HOW PURE WORKS?
Everything starts with Personal Ads. To see other people in the feed, you need to post your Ad. Write what kind of experience you are looking for and find someone who would share the same experience with you. Be creative and original with your ads, that's always appealing.

* IN PURE ALL BORDERS ARE OPEN
Paris, New-York or London? You can check any city worldwide and meet people from PURE community from around the globe.  

* WHAT HAPPENS IN PURE STAYS IN PURE
Photos self-destruct right after being seen, and in case someone takes a screenshot, you will get a notification about that. Also, all chat messages, including photos and audio, shared in chats cannot be saved to the phone's gallery.

* OUR MISSION IS TO KEEP PURE A PURE EXPERIENCE
Safety of our community is one of our key priorities. We are constantly improving our algorithms to find and get rid of scam and spam accounts, also our system sends automatic alerts on trigger words that might be used by scammers, so don't be surprised in case you will get a warning. 
Keep chatting anonymously via PURE and do not switch to other messengers. You know what they say: better safe than sorry. 

PURE uses auto-renewing subscriptions — you have to subscribe to get inside.
Here’s what you should know about PURE subscriptions:

- If you choose to purchase a weekly, monthly or annual subscription you will be able to go online and interact via chats with other users during the chosen subscription period. The prices may vary per country and are subject to change with a notice. Prices are clearly displayed in the app.
- All subscriptions renew automatically unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period without any limitations.
- Auto-renewal can be canceled at any time by going to your settings in the Apple Store after the purchase.
- All personal data is handled under PURE’s privacy policy https://pure.app/content/en/privacy

You can add access control devices to check the current status of doors and view unlock records, as well as perform remote unlocking operations on the doors.

Together with your connected Philips Air device, Air+ provides a smart experience that ensures you breathe clean and healthy air.

The app keeps track of all indoor and outdoor pollutants and automatically adjust your device’s performance, so you don’t have to. Air+ keeps you in control, at home or away, with a device remote and notifications about all your air concerns including pollutants, allergies and gas. And by staying in the know with insights into your air quality data from past to present, you are in full control of breathing the clean, healthy air you deserve.


Auto Plus mode - the smartest way to clean air
Once you activate Auto Plus mode in the Air+ app, your indoor air will automatically be cleaned to 
keep pollutants at bay. This Self-adaptive Technology, powered by Artificial Intelligence, considers 
the readings of the smart sensors, room size, outdoor data and behavioral patterns to maximize 
performance. 

Disclaimer: Auto Plus mode will be released in winter 2022 for most Philips Air devices.


Get to the core of air quality
Thanks to the smart device sensors, Air+ provides you with real-time, indoor air quality data. Ranging from high-level snapshots to detailed views, all data is available to you up until a year ago. More information about each pollutant and their causes are included so you can make well informed decisions about your indoor air.

In full control of your air, at home or away
Air+ features a built-in remote so you are in full control of your device’s performance. Seamlessly 
switch between different modes, fan speeds and other features to tailor the device settings to your 
needs. Great for turning your device off when you’re away or on when you’re heading home, or to
make changes without being near your Air device.

Easy upkeep for maximized output
Air+ tracks when it’s time to clean or replace certain parts of you Air device to make sure it runs at 
peak performance. Messaging and notifications alert you when the low-effort maintenance should 
be taken care of, and Air+ has step-by-step instructions handy if you need them. Plus, in most cases, 
you can buy new filters straight from the app.

A holistic air quality experience with outdoor data
As outdoor air quality can have a big impact on the indoor levels, Air+ includes a comprehensive 
overview of real-time outdoor readings. Additionally, Air+ provides a quick snapshot of the current 
weather at each location. You can add up to five cities to keep you in the know about the air quality 
conditions near and far.

Air+ also supports a smarter experience with Philips Robot Vacuum Cleaners.
